sequenceDiagram
    participant Hub as Hub Container
    participant Queue as Task Queue
    participant Worker as Worker Container
    participant Workspace as Workspace Lease

    Hub->>Queue: Claim next delegated task
    Queue-->>Hub: Task metadata + scope
    Hub->>Worker: Assign task with execution_scope
    Worker->>Workspace: Acquire isolated workspace
    Worker->>Worker: Execute plan node locally
    Worker-->>Hub: Output + trace_id + verification payload
    Worker->>Workspace: Cleanup / release lease
    Hub->>Hub: Persist provenance and audit hash chain
